# users.http
### create
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "u101",
    "password": "changeit",
    "role": "USER"
}

### create 2
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "u102",
    "password": "changeit",
    "role": "USER"
}

### create 3
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "u103",
    "password": "changeit",
    "role": "USER"
