### get
GET http://localhost:3000/users/u101

### get with valid token
GET http://localhost:3000/users/u101
Authorization: Bearer VALID_TOKEN

### get with invalid token
GET http://localhost:3000/users/u101
Authorization: Bearer INVALID_TOKEN


### get - invalid path
GET http://localhost:3000/users/100

### get - invalid path with Authorization
GET http://localhost:3000/users/u
Authorization: Bearer VALID_TOKEN
